!play
@SpaceTraveler check your DMs for instructions on how to play! Please note that after 10 minutes of inactivity you'll need to start over.

There's a new way for _everyone_ to earn some points... but warning... it's ***hard***... 😬 

Type `!play` in here and then check your DMs for a message from `Eco Story Bot`. 

You'll be introduced to a quest. It's painful and annoying (just like interacting with banks). But if you make it through... a random amount of :points: will be yours! (And, by the way: the rewards will be reduced over time...)

Major kudos to @KingSuper for building it and @Bryce  | Eco for writing the story!
